  "texts": [
    "Detecting unusual behavior or unexpected events in sensor data can help identify potential faults, intrusions, or environmental changes, enabling timely responses and preventive actions.",
    "Traditional rule-based and statistical anomaly detection methods are not very effective in dynamic and complex WSN environments.",
    "Therefore, more advanced and adaptive anomaly detection techniques are necessary to address the changing challenges in WSNs.",
    "Background and MotivationMachine Learning (ML) has proven to be highly effective in improving anomaly detection capabilities in various domains in recent years as researched by Mahesh et. al in [2].",
    "The ability of ML algorithms to learn patterns and relationships from data makes them ideal for detecting anomalies in WSNs."
  ],
